Class GameManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.GameManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CreationGameObservable
    public class GameManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements CreationGameObservable
    A game manager contains a lobby and the match associated to it. It's the entity that has to instantiate and control both the lobby and match and contains all the logic that links them.
